如果在这之前scanResponseTable已经移除了,  processResponseCommand()就不能向ResponseFuture里面添加response,
 然后ChannelFutureListener会把ResponseFuture.setSendRequestOK设成true, scanResponseTable再执行回调, response 是null, 但是sendRequestOK是true, 就会抛出这个异常MQClientException ex = new MQClientException("unknow reseaon", responseFuture.getCause());
